&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who are we?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Qualio, the engineering department is responsible for the &quot;what&quot; and the &quot;how&quot;. &quot;What&quot; as in what should we build for our customers. &quot;How&quot; as in how do we delivery and operate the solution.&lt;/p&gt;
