&lt;p&gt;We are designing our teams to own specific horizontal areas of our application. Teams are made up of a Product manager (PM), Engineering team lead and a team of engineers. Owning the area of application means everything, collaborating with product managers, customer success partners, architecture, peer engineering teams to deliver robust cloud-based solutions that drive powerful experiences to our customers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As Werner Vogels says, &quot;You build it, you run it&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What do we value?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In order to make this a reality we value a number of things:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Iterative development - Solutions are delivered as a collection of small pieces. No big bangs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Test driven development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clean code&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Automation in all its forms - tests, infrastructure, build and deploy - everything&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&quot;Done&quot; means it&#39;s in the hands of customers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
